WHAT IS IT?
The Updoots Adder Chrome extension is built to add your favorite Internet URLs in organized bookmarks or folders within your updoots.com account.

Makes for saving your favorite internet links easy while browsing the web. Just create an account at updoots.com and login into the chrome extension. Simply add the URL to the folder of your choice. Visit updoots.com to go back to those URLs you saved.
